= Instructions for running these scripts. 

You need to add this directory to your path if you want to run *LSDTopoTools* from the command line. 

You can https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14637979/how-to-permanently-set-path-on-linux-unix[edit your `.bashrc` file]. 

Or you can https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/23426/how-to-alter-path-within-a-shell-script[spawn a new shell] with the correct paths.